name: imadethese
description:
I made six games because I am insane.

Box Barrage -

Space to jump. Don't hit boxes. You have three lives.

Fish Fiasco -

Catch the fish with your mouse! Don't let them fall! You have three lives.

S**t Skydiving -

Land in the water, not on the ground! Arrow keys to move left and right. You have one chance!

Flying Fred -

Space to fly. It is Flappy Bird.

Why's Waldoo -

Click the red person. THEN YOU GET EVERY POINT.

Pitiful Pet -

Feed the person water and food with the arrow keys. Don't over or under feed them and make them grow big and strong.
